'''''Tjitji: Umukobwa wa Himba''''', ni filime ngufi ya Namibiya yasohotsemuri 2015 iyobowe na Oshosheni Hiveluahkandi yakozwe na Virginia Witts<ref>https://www.baslerafrika.ch/projects/hiveluah-oshosheni/</ref>.  Iyi filime yibanze ku buzima bwa Tjijandjeua 'Tjitji', umunyeshuri ukiri muto, watsinze kandi wifuza cyane Himba ufite inzozi zâ€™ibanga zo kuzaba icyamamare 'Talk Show Host'. Iyi filime yamenyekanye kubera guca imyumvire ku bagore.<ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/201511181238.html</ref><ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/201410270508.html</ref>   

Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime<ref>https://www.psp-culture.com/culture/immersed-in-the-art-of-film-making/</ref>. Iyi filime yari ifite nomination mu byiciro Umuyobozi mwiza, Amashusho yumwimerere meza, amanota meza yumuziki wumwimerere, Cinematografi nziza, na Filime Nziza Nziza muri [[Namibian]] Theatre na Film Awards 2014 yabereye muri Theatre yigihugu ya Namibiya (NTN)<ref>https://www.namibian.com.na/print.php?id=129955&type=2</ref><ref>https://nfc.na/namibian/</ref>.  Nyuma, yatsindiye ibihembo bya cinematografi na firime yerekana inkuru muri Namibian Theatre na Film Awards muri 2014.<ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/201410270508.html</ref>  Yakiriwe neza mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Bangalore ryabereye i Bangalore, mu Buhinde mu 2015. ''Tjitji Umukobwa wa Himba na we'' yari filime ngufi ku mugaragaro mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Afurika muri 2015.<ref>https://www.africavenir.org/fr/details-evenement/cal/event/detail/2015/12/05/inspiring_young_imaginations_screening_tjitji/view-list%7Cpage_id-765%7Coffset-4.html?tx_cal_controller%255Bcategory%255D=10&cHash=b2978b38d01f34fa5450926539d7e132</ref> 

